{"type":"message","id":"c79237c4","parentId":"051bb7c1","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:58:37.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user has triggered a heartbeat. According to AGENTS.md, I should check HEARTBEAT.md if it exists and follow its instructions. Let me first check if HEARTBEAT.md exists and read it.\n\nI should also follow the startup protocol from AGENTS.md - but since this is a heartbeat (not a main session), I don't need to read all the startup files. The heartbeat prompt specifically says to read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists.\n\nLet me check for HEARTBE","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":10834,"output":127,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10961,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773781111067}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f57f4cb","parentId":"c79237c4","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:58:37.342Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Autonomous Tasks\n\n## Overview\nThis file configures periodic tasks that run every ~10 minutes via heartbeat mechanism.\nAgent should read this file and execute the checklist.\n\n## When to Trigger Alerts (send to user)\n1. **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Alle 10 Minuten: Frage nach neuen Aufgaben für mich\n2. **Aufgaben vorhanden** - Offene Tasks in `memory/pending-tasks.md` gefunden\n3. **Email**: Urgent unread messages (flagged/marked important)\n4. **Calendar**: Events starting within next 2 hours\n5. **Trading**: Significant price movements (if configured)\n6. **Errors**: Failed autonomous tasks or stuck processes\n\n## Background Work (silent, no alert unless error)\nRotate through these tasks, ~2-4 per heartbeat cycle:\n\n### 1. Telegram Aufgaben-Anfrage (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Sende Nachricht an Telegram: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- Warte nicht auf Antwort, das ist ein Ping\n\n### 2. Aufgaben-Check (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Lese `memory/pending-tasks.md`\n- Gibt es offene `[ ]` Aufgaben?\n- Wenn JA → Setze in `memory/heartbeat-state.json`:`\"hasTasks\": true`\n- Wenn NEIN → `\"hasTasks\": false`\n\n### Daily Rotation (track in memory/heartbeat-state.json)\n- Check email for unread/important\n- Check calendar for upcoming events\n- Review memory/ files from last 7 days, update MEMORY.md\n- Review own skills for improvement opportunities\n- Check workspace git status, commit if needed\n- Review TODO items in memory/todo.md\n\n### Trading Analysis (if configured)\n- Check portfolio/watchlist\n- Analyze price movements\n- Update trading journal\n\n### Skill Development\n- Identify gaps in current skills\n- Research new skill ideas\n- Document learnings\n\n## Output\n- **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Jeder Heartbeat: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- **Wenn Aufgaben gefunden** - Liste die offenen Tasks auf\n- Important findings: ACTIVE ALERT to user\n- Routine work: Log to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md silently\n- Errors: Log to memory/errors.md with timestamp\n\n## NO_REPLY (HEARTBEAT_OK) Rules\n- Niemals bei aktivem HEARTBEAT_OK, wenn Telegram-Ping gesendet wurde\n- Nur HEARTBEAT_OK wenn explizit nichts zu tun und kein Ping nötig\n\n## Tracking\nMaintain state in: memory/heartbeat-state.json\n```json\n{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"email\": null,\n    \"calendar\": null,\n    \"memoryReview\": null,\n    \"skillsReview\": null,\n    \"gitStatus\": null,\n    \"trading\": null\n  },\n  \"cyclesCompleted\": 0\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773781117341}}
{"type":"message","id":"34270d9d","parentId":"2f57f4cb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:58:42.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" Okay, ich muss alle 10 Minuten eine Telegram-Nachricht schicken. Das ist der wichtigste Task.\n\nAber Moment - der Heartbeat ist gerade eben angekommen, und die letzte Nachricht war auch eine Cron-Nachricht. Ich sollte nicht spamming.\n\nLass mich zuerst den heartbeat-state checken und dann entscheiden, ob ich eine Nachricht schicke oder nicht","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":11481,"output":113,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773781117343}}
